<p>10月19日，量子通信板块全天强势，截止收盘，<span>中信国安（000839.SZ）</span>、<span>蓝盾股份（300297.SZ）</span>、<span>浩丰科技（300419.SZ）</span>、<span>科大国创（300520.SZ）</span>、<span>光库科技（300620.SZ）</span>和<span>盛洋科技（603703.SH）</span>等涨停。</p>
<p><img src="//p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201019/fe16c97fca12409796e72f988051b2e5.png" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
